verbose_text: Notably, the mRNA level of AHNAK2 was enhanced significantly in human ccRCC samples as compared to their adjacent normal renal tissues (Beroukhim Renal, n = 32, fold change = 9.856, p < 0.001; Grumz Renal, n = 10, fold change = 15.044, p < 0.001; Jones Renal, n = 23, fold change = 4.128, p < 0.001; Lenburg Renal, n = 9, fold change = 5.854, p < 0.001; Figure XREF_FIG B).
